config LGUEST_GUEST
	bool "Lguest guest support"
	select PARAVIRT
	depends on !X86_PAE
	select VIRTIO_RING
	help
	  Lguest is a tiny in-kernel hypervisor.  Selecting this will
	  allow your kernel to boot under lguest.  This option will increase
	  your kernel size by about 6k.  If in doubt, say N.
